title: Watch: Dog chauffeur takes toddler for a spin in toy car
text:
If this family can train Daisy to feed and change their son Oliver's nappies, they'll save themselves a fortune in childminding fees.
In case you're wondering, the boy's mother Jessica Wolf is the one in charge of the speed of the car but the steering is all Daisy.
At least we know how that 'Driving Miss Daisy' reboot is going to go.
Via YouTube
